Mechel Emissions in Chelyabinsk to Be Probed, Vedomosti Says

-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 
2011-08-25T04:27:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/mechel-emissions-in-chelyabinsk-to-be-probed-vedomosti-says.html
 Mikhail Yurevich, governor of
 Russia ’s Chelyabinsk region, ordered a probe of gas emissions at
two plants, including an OAO Mechel metallurgical factory,
 Vedomosti  reported.  The plants include Mechel’s  Chelyabinsk Metallurgical Plant (CHMK) 
and the Chelyabinsk Electro-Metallurgical Complex, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow 
